[Amit Varma]: taken enough of your time and you've been very kind with your time and insights. I'm

03:50:03.200 --> 03:50:09.200
[Amit Varma]: going to ask you one final question, which I can't help but ask, which I ask all my guests.

03:50:09.200 --> 03:50:13.200
