03:50:13.200 --> 03:50:17.200
[Amit Varma]: shaped you, changed you in some way that are dear to you, or even books where you want

03:50:17.200 --> 03:50:23.200
[Amit Varma]: to stand on a soapbox and shout, read this book, please read this book.

03:50:23.200 --> 03:50:31.200
