03:50:31.200 --> 03:50:37.200
[Guest]: talking about? Like, I would not recommend, you know, Guha's India After Gandhi or many

03:50:37.200 --> 03:50:42.200
[Guest]: of his books, because I think he, because his wealth of knowledge is so immense, he

03:50:42.200 --> 03:50:47.200
