03:50:47.200 --> 03:50:52.200
[Guest]: to you in 10,000. So India After Gandhi can tell you a lot about the odds that India was

03:50:52.200 --> 03:50:59.200
[Guest]: shaped in with, in a fairly, I mean, think about how big the country is, keeping that

03:50:59.200 --> 03:51:04.200
[Guest]: in mind. So, you know, but I would not recommend that to someone who's in class 10, 11, 12,

03:51:04.200 --> 03:51:08.200
[Guest]: or even first year college. Maybe you should read that if you're in your 20s or 30s. I

03:51:08.200 --> 03:51:13.200
[Guest]: would not recommend Thomas Hardy to anyone who's maybe mid to late 20s.

