[Amit Varma]: I love PG Woodhouse but continue.

03:51:27.200 --> 03:51:37.200
[Guest]: Yeah, but yeah, I would recommend, you know, honestly, I read a lot for my age. So I actually

03:51:37.200 --> 03:51:43.200
[Guest]: wouldn't. But what I will say is that books that have completely knocked my socks off

03:51:43.200 --> 03:51:50.200
[Guest]: is M and the Big Whom by Jerry Pinto. I think, and you know, I've read some other books

03:51:50.200 --> 03:51:56.200
